Note:
This file handles system call permission validation and OS-level access control for the Runa runtime services.

This file performs the following tasks:
- Process system call permission validation and OS-level access control
- Handle syscall permission checking and system resource access validation
- Manage system-level permission enforcement and security policy validation
- Process system permission error handling and access denial feedback

This file is essential because of the following reasons:
- permission_checker enables comprehensive system call permission validation and OS-level access control
- Proper system permission handling ensures correct OS-level security enforcement and user experience
- permission_checker support enables Runa compilation for secure system call workflows

This file consists of the following functions/features/operation types:
- System call permission validation and OS-level access control
- Syscall permission checking and system resource access validation
- System-level permission enforcement and security policy validation
- System permission error handling and access denial feedback
:End Note

